<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>488</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ shēn shēn de zhù fú nǐ 迦南488</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ shēn shēn de zhù fú nǐ men, bǐ cǐ xiāng ài yǒng bù fēn.
 jìng wèi shén xiào shuāng qīn, yòng ài xīn duì dài rén.
 yī xīn lái jiē nà, hù xiāng lái guān xīn,
 yào xǐng wù zhēn xī guāng yīn, yīn yīn qín qín fú shì rén.
 shén de cì fú, dōu dāng jǐn běn fēn.
 zhǔ shì wǒ men jiān gù pán shí, wú suǒ jù pà xiàng qián jìn.</lyrics>
</song>